author: @sharrrrr
text:
0:45 - 0:55 These 10 seconds are the vital part that explains the connection of all (current) units of NCT.

After we saw a brief shot of all NCT 2018 members, a door opened, by Taeyong (the leader of NCT), to NCT Dream who were waiting for us (editing this in 2024: remember NCT Dream has a line that says "Welcome, we've been waiting for you" in Hello Future lyrics) before clips of WayV MV starts playing. It seems like a mere aesthetic to some people but after I rewatch NCTmentary from 2018, I realized it's a metaphor for NCT concept.

Some narrative from NCTmentary:
NCT are connected by their dreams. There's a deeper dream called dream in a dream where the dreams are often strange and felt like a reality. Like a vision instead of a dream. Then we have Kun telling us about his "spectacular dream". This dream in a dream stage is where the synchronization of dreams happens in order to create a reality. 

Why NCT Dream behind the door?
Coz they are the NCT Dream, the dream that connect every unit of NCT. They are going to connect us from NCT 2018 to WayV. 

After the dream (NCT Dream) there's a deeper dream called Dream In A Dream (aka Ten's solo for SM Station). That's why there's a huge Ten solo shot at 0:51 and a hint of Dream In A Dream MV we'll talk about shortly. 

The vision-like deeper dream. Guess what WayV stands for?
We are your Vision.

Kun's spectacular vision-like dream. Guess who WayV leader is?
Kun. Because the Vision (aka WayV) is the spectacular dream he was talking about. 

So let me explain this chronologically. 
After we meet NCT Dream behind the door, at 0:48 we have this eye shot of Jeno, the marbles from NCTmentary Dream Lab video, the water drop from Dream In A Dream MV, scenes from WayV's Regular MV, and a close up of Jaehyun. 

The marbles remind us that the following scenes are explained in NCTmentary. 

Jeno is from NCT Dream and through his eye we're entering his head to access the dream, and the water drop is like "Welcome to the deeper dream called Dream In A Dream" (also do y'all hear "Warning: Entering system" or something when the water drops? we ARE entering the deeper dream) where then we meet Ten (the host of Dream In A Dream stage) and WayV (the Vision). Then we go back to reality, exiting the dream-vision stage through Jaehyun's eyes to start the NCT 2020 era.

Why Jaehyun? My guess is, if NCT Dream is the dream and WayV is the vision, then the rest of them are the reality. Coz what I understand from NCTmentary, the whole concept of NCT narrative is to connect dreams to create a vision and manifesting it until it becomes a reality. Where did they start to manifest their dreams into reality? Seoul, South Korea, longitude coordinate 127Â° and NCT 127 is the unit that Jaehyun is in.

Conclusion: SM never fails to amaze me. Easter eggs after easter eggs all these years. That makes Ten's Dream In A Dream solo isn't just him participating in SM Station. It's a hint that Ten is going to be in the Vision unit of NCT which is WayV. And shame on those who said WayV is not a part of NCT. WayV belongs in NCT since the very start even before SM introduce WayV to the public.

author: @mohamedn6934
text:
#Virus_Corona_Adalah_Sebahagian_Azab_Yang_Lebih_Kecil
#Obat_Penyembuhan_Dari_Corona

Petikan dari bayan keterangan yang ditulis oleh Al Imam Al Mahdi Al Muntadhar, Nasser Mohammed Al Yamani, beserta tarikh dan tajuk keterangan:

19 - 05 - 2020
Virus Corona dan bayan keterangan pemutus yang sebenar, pemisah antara yang hak dan yang batil, bukan senda gurauan..

Petikan keterangan:

Demikian itu agar kalian sadar akan kadar kemampuan diri kalian, juga supaya kalian tahu dengan pasti, bahawa penyakit azab seksaan yang mencekik dari Allah ini, yang kalian namakannya virus Corona, sama sekali tidak ada yang akan menghilangkannya dari kalian selain Allah yang Maha Esa semata-mata

Maka dari itu hendaklah mereka bertaubat dari dosa-dosa besar, dari perkara-perkara yang keji, menganiaya, menindas dan menzalimi manusia, dan dari kezaliman syirik, hendaklah mereka mengucapkan:

"Wahai Tuhan kami, sesungguhnya kami ini telah menzalimi diri kami sendiri, dan sekiranya Engkau tidak mengampuni kami dan memberi rahmat kepada kami, nescaya kami termasuk kalangan orang-orang yang merugi"

Setelah bertaubat kepada Allah dan kembali pada-Nya, hendaklah mereka mengucapkan:

"Ya Allah, sesungguhnya aku ini adalah hamba-Mu, aku mohon dengan hak Laa ilaaha illaa Anta -tiada tuhan yang berhak disembah kecuali Engkau- dengan hak rahmat-Mu yang telah Engkau tetapkan ke atas Diri-Mu, dengan hak besarnya nikmat keredhaan Diri-Mu yang teragung, yang lebih besar dari kenikmatan syurga-Mu, aku mohon sembuhkanlah aku ini dari azab seksaan Corona atau singkirkannya dariku, sesungguhnya kami ini percaya pada penyeru kebenaran dari sisi-Mu"

"Ya Allah, lenyapkanlah dari kami ini azab seksaan-Mu yang datang dari segala macam rupa, agar kami ini dapat mengikuti jalan yang hak dari sisi-Mu, kami mohon teguhkanlah keikhlasan dan kesetiaan kami terhadap perkara yang telah kami janjikan kepada-Mu, wahai Dzat yang membatasi antara manusia dan hatinya, Dzat yang Maha Berkuasa mengubah dan menyekat di antara manusia dan pekerjaan hatinya, tiadalah bagi kami harapan selain dari mengharap pada rahmat-Mu yang telah Engkau tetapkan ke atas Diri-Mu, sekiranya Engkau tidak mengampuni kami dan memberi rahmat kepada kami, nescaya kami termasuk kalangan orang-orang yang merugi"

"Ya Allah, sesungguhnya Engkau telah berfirman dalam muhkam Kitab-Mu:Berdoalah kepada-Ku, niscaya akan Kuperkenankan bagimu [Ghaafir:60], maka terimalah dariku permohonanku dan taubatku kembali pada-Mu, dan dari-Mu aku mengharapkan agar Engkau memperkenankannya, sesungguhnya Engkau tidak menyalahi janji-Mu, wahai Tuhan kami, Maha Suci Engkau, janji-Mu benar dan Engkau-lah yang paling pengasih dari sekalian yang mengasihani"

"Ya Allah, teguhkanlah keikhlasan dan kesetiaan kami terhadap perkara yang telah kami janjikan kepada-Mu, untuk mengikuti orang yang menyeru kami ke jalan Allah, dengan seruan dakwah yang berkumandang di seluruh dunia, dari khalifah Allah di bumi Al Imam Al Mahdi Nasser Mohammed Al Yamani"

"Ya Allah, jadikanlah perutusannya sebagai suatu nikmat anugerah untuk kami, bukan sebagai kemurkaan dan dendam terhadap kami, disebabkan keberpalingan kami dari seruan dakwah yang hak, oleh Al Imam Al Mahdi Nasser Mohammed Al Yamani"

Barangsiapa yang menolak untuk berdoa dengan doa ini, maka pasti kelak mereka akan ditimpakan dengan azab seksaan yang kalian namakannya sebagai virus Corona

Selesai petikan
Bayan keterangan selengkapnya pada pautan ini:

Ini adalah pautan bayan keterangan Al Imam Al Mahdi Nasser Mohammed Al Yamani mengenai Corona, sebelum ianya diumumkan oleh Organisasi Kesehatan Dunia (WHO), sebagai wabak yang melanda seluruh dunia, pandemik global, sekitar kurang lebih seminggu setelah bayan keterangan dikeluarkan, dengan tarikh dan tajuk:

Virus Corona adalah sebahagian azab yang lebih kecil sebelum kedatangan azab yang lebih besar, mudah-mudahan mereka kembali ke jalan yang benar..

Maka dari itu hendaklah mereka bertaubat dari dosa-dosa besar, dari perkara-perkara yang keji, menganiaya, menindas dan menzalimi manusia, dan dari kezaliman syirik, hendaklah mereka mengucapkan:

"Wahai Tuhan kami, sesungguhnya kami ini telah menzalimi diri kami sendiri, dan sekiranya Engkau tidak mengampuni kami dan memberi rahmat kepada kami, nescaya kami termasuk kalangan orang-orang yang merugi"

Setelah bertaubat kepada Allah dan kembali pada-Nya, hendaklah mereka mengucapkan:

"Ya Allah, sesungguhnya aku ini adalah hamba-Mu, aku mohon dengan hak Laa ilaaha illaa Anta -tiada tuhan yang berhak disembah kecuali Engkau- dengan hak rahmat-Mu yang telah Engkau tetapkan ke atas Diri-Mu, dengan hak besarnya nikmat keredhaan Diri-Mu yang teragung, yang lebih besar dari kenikmatan syurga-Mu, aku mohon sembuhkanlah aku ini dari azab seksaan Corona atau singkirkannya dariku, sesungguhnya kami ini percaya pada penyeru kebenaran dari sisi-Mu"

"Ya Allah, lenyapkanlah dari kami ini azab seksaan-Mu yang datang dari segala macam rupa, agar kami ini dapat mengikuti jalan yang hak dari sisi-Mu, kami mohon teguhkanlah keikhlasan dan kesetiaan kami terhadap perkara yang telah kami janjikan kepada-Mu, wahai Dzat yang membatasi antara manusia dan hatinya, Dzat yang Maha Berkuasa mengubah dan menyekat di antara manusia dan pekerjaan hatinya, tiadalah bagi kami harapan selain dari mengharap pada rahmat-Mu yang telah Engkau tetapkan ke atas Diri-Mu, sekiranya Engkau tidak mengampuni kami dan memberi rahmat kepada kami, nescaya kami termasuk kalangan orang-orang yang merugi"

"Ya Allah, sesungguhnya Engkau telah berfirman dalam muhkam Kitab-Mu:Berdoalah kepada-Ku, niscaya akan Kuperkenankan bagimu [Ghaafir:60], maka terimalah dariku permohonanku dan taubatku kembali pada-Mu, dan dari-Mu aku mengharapkan agar Engkau memperkenankannya, sesungguhnya Engkau tidak menyalahi janji-Mu, wahai Tuhan kami, Maha Suci Engkau, janji-Mu benar dan Engkau-lah yang paling pengasih dari sekalian yang mengasihani"

"Ya Allah, teguhkanlah keikhlasan dan kesetiaan kami terhadap perkara yang telah kami janjikan kepada-Mu, untuk mengikuti orang yang menyeru kami ke jalan Allah, dengan seruan dakwah yang berkumandang di seluruh dunia, dari khalifah Allah di bumi Al Imam Al Mahdi Nasser Mohammed Al Yamani"

"Ya Allah, jadikanlah perutusannya sebagai suatu nikmat anugerah untuk kami, bukan sebagai kemurkaan dan dendam terhadap kami, disebabkan keberpalingan kami dari seruan dakwah yang hak, oleh Al Imam Al Mahdi Nasser Mohammed Al Yamani"

Barangsiapa yang menolak untuk berdoa dengan doa ini, maka pasti kelak mereka akan ditimpakan dengan azab seksaan yang kalian namakannya sebagai virus Corona

author: @sarahberlaud4285
text:
THIS. This is what we've been hoping, waiting, and praying for... I know SM has a lot of problems, just like any big company, but I really want to say a heartfelt thank you to the people who made this happen behind the scenes, too. It's brave and wonderful to set aside politics and any negative things about WayV not being a "real" part of NCT (although there were, of course, allusions to that, like when they said that NCT had 21 members... but they wouldn't *directly* say that WayV was NCT...). I feel so, SO happy... as soon as I saw WayV mvs included in this, I really teared up. 

Of course the ones we stan are the boys themselves, and they deserve the entire WORLD <3 But on days like these, I also kinda stan whoever finally made this happen, too <3

author: @riz823
text: NCT 2020 is the first time that all the NCT members will be coming together since NCT 2018 two years ago. For this grand comeback, the boys have released an equally grand time table. On September 21st (today), NCT 2020 is revealing their logo and timeline. From there, they'll be revealing their year party video on the 22nd, reveal 'The Past' image and have a live event on the 23rd, reveal 'The Future' image on the 24th, reveal 'The Past & Future' video on the 25th, drop teaser images on the 28th, 29th, 30th, and October 1st, reveal album details on October 2nd, release their 'Deja Vu' track video on October 8th, release their 'Misfit' track video on the 9th, release their 'Make a Wish' MV teaser on the 10th, and release their album on the 12th. But that's not the end! They'll be releasing a teaser for 'From Home' on the 18th, and then release the MV for 'From Home' on the 19th.

author: @ratnaghosh7690
text:
ok so this news came out like 15 hours ago...and i am seeing now. i am not an nctzen, but i try to keep up with all SM news. Seems like 2 new members- Shotaro and Sungchan will be joining NCT 2020. This is not s sub-unit ones. NCT had 21 members until yesterday. But they never had a song with all 21 members. they performed in sub-units like WAY-V, NCT Dream, NCT-U and NCT 127. So now 2 more members so OT 23. Now this is the first time ever they are gonna perform all together. SM Entertainment announced that NCT 2020 will include the 21 members of NCT 127, NCT Dream, and WayV, along with two new members Shotaro and Sungchan who will be joining a new NCT team that will be launched in the future. Through NCT U, the 23 members will team up in various combinations and pull off diverse concepts. So yeah a great day. at 8:30 pm india 20th Sep which is midnight, 12 pm kst korea of 21st Sep, NCT official twiiter account posted it. I am an Exo-L. Today is CHEN'S birthday. it Midnight korea today got 2 imp things. Chen birthday and NCT new album news. 
so yes at 8:30 20th September india, EXO CHEN turned 28 and NCT news came. the timing is so perfect. The NCT news was released in twitter at dot 8:30, which is dot 12 pm in korea, marking 21st September. I love the timing.
though i am not NCTZEN i will support them.

NCT 2018 was project that united the boys from all units to form thier first full album.

text:
Hi? In case someone's new here, 
here's the guideline to the âœ¨ *neo culture technology !* âœ¨ :
â€”NCT (ì—”ì‹œí‹°) is a South Korean boy group formed by SM Entertainment. Their name stands for the Hallyu localization project Neo Culture Technology, a term coined by their producer and SM founder Lee Soo-man to describe the group's concept of having an unlimited number of members divided into multiple sub-units based in various cities worldwide. (Â©Â® wikipedia) 

the members :  Name (sub-unit) 
ps: i don't put nct u since its members dpeemd on the concept~

â€¢ Lee Taeyong = Taeyong (127)
â€¢ Moon Taeil.  = Taeil (127)
â€¢ Seo Johnny = Johnny (127) 
â€¢ Nakamoto Yuta = Yuta (127)
â€¢ Qian Kun      = Kun (Wayv) 
â€¢ Kim Doyoung = Doyoung (127)
â€¢ Chittaphon leechaiyapornkul = Ten (Wayv) 
â€¢ Jung Jaehyun = Jaehyun (127)
â€¢ Dong Sicheng = Winwin (127, Wayv) 
â€¢ Kim Jungwoo = Jungwoo (127)
â€¢ Huang xuxi, Wong Yukhei 
= Lucas (Wayv) 
â€¢ Lee Mark = (127, Dream) 
â€¢ Xiao De Jun = Xiaojun (Wayv) 
â€¢ Huang Guanheng = Hendery (Wayv) 
â€¢ Huang Renjun = Renjun (Dream) 
â€¢ Lee Jeno = Jeno (Dream) 
â€¢ Lee Donghyuck = Haechan (Dream) 
â€¢Na Jaemin = Jaemin (Dream) 
â€¢ Liu YangYang = YangYang (Wayv) 
â€¢ Zhong Chenle = Chenle (Dream) 
â€¢ Park Jisung = Jisung (Dream)

â€”NCT U is the first NCT sub unit debuted with "The 7th Sense" song. It has different members every comeback because its members depend on the concept of the song. 

â€”NCT 127 is the second sub unit debuted with "Fire Truck" song. It has 7 members at first, and then Johnny and Doyoung joined, and then Jungwoo joined so now they are 10.

â€”NCT Dream is the third sub unit debuted with "Chewing Gum" with 7 members. In case you don't know, at first nct dream used a gradutional system that means if the member is already 20 years old they had to graduate from NCT Dream. But on 14th April, the graduation system had been erased. 

â€”Wayv is the last sub unit debuted with "Regular : Chinese Ver." song. It's a sub-unit based in China and has 7 members.

author: @Kammy_-ez8jx
text: Please even if you don't like to stream/vote, just know that it really helps NCT with music show wins/end of year awards. I want to see them win a daesang someday, but our fandom just needs a push when it comes to streaming. We as a fandom are amazing with album sales. Like really really good. For those that cannot buy albums, you can still support by taking whatever free time you have to stream and vote if you feel comfortable doing that. This cb can be monumental for NCT as we saw with NCT 2018, their popularity increased immensely, so I know a lot of new fans will be joining. If we collectively have the mindset that we are just a lazy fandom, then tbh that's not really productive and also not good for new fans:/ Ik we can get stuff done, but we just procrastinate so much and do everything at the last minute lol. So please let's all really hype this cb but also make sure to enjoy every second of it:)
